# REST Client Test File (for VS Code REST Client extension)

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### Register User
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!@",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "phone": "+27123456789"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePass123!@"
}

### Verify Token
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Change Password
POST http://localhost:3001/api/auth/change-password
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "oldPassword": "SecurePass123!@",
  "newPassword": "NewSecurePass123!@",
  "confirmPassword": "NewSecurePass123!@"
}

### Get User Profile
GET http://localhost:3001/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update User Profile
PUT http://localhost:3001/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Updated",
  "lastName": "Name",
  "phone": "+27987654321",
  "country": "ZA",
  "city": "Cape Town",
  "address": "123 Main St"
}

### Initiate KYC Verification
POST http://localhost:3001/api/kyc/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Check KYC Status
GET http://localhost:3001/api/kyc/status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Submit KYC Documents
POST http://localhost:3001/api/kyc/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "documentType": "NATIONAL_ID",
  "documentNumber": "1234567890",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User",
  "dateOfBirth": "1990-01-15",
  "idDocumentUrl": "https://example.com/id.jpg",
  "proofOfAddressUrl": "https://example.com/proof.jpg"
}

### Create Stripe Payment Intent
POST http://localhost:3001/api/payment/stripe/intent
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "currency": "ZAR"
}

### Confirm Stripe Payment
POST http://localhost:3001/api/payment/stripe/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "{{transactionId}}",
  "paymentIntentId": "{{paymentIntentId}}"
}

### Add Payment Method
POST http://localhost:3001/api/payment/method
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "CARD",
  "cardToken": "tok_visa"
}

### Initiate PayFast Payment
POST http://localhost:3001/api/payment/payfast/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 50.00,
  "itemName": "AfriCoin Deposit",
  "itemDescription": "Deposit funds to account"
}

### Get All Transactions
GET http://localhost:3001/api/transaction
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Transaction by ID
GET http://localhost:3001/api/transaction/{{transactionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Transaction Summary
GET http://localhost:3001/api/transaction/summary/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel Transaction
POST http://localhost:3001/api/transaction/{{transactionId}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Refund Transaction
POST http://localhost:3001/api/payment/{{transactionId}}/refund
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer request"
}

### Get Payment Methods
GET http://localhost:3001/api/user/payment-methods
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete Payment Method
DELETE http://localhost:3001/api/user/payment-methods/{{paymentMethodId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Set Default Payment Method
PATCH http://localhost:3001/api/user/payment-methods/{{paymentMethodId}}/default
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Create Solana Wallet
POST http://localhost:3001/api/solana/wallet/create
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Solana Wallet Balance
GET http://localhost:3001/api/solana/wallet/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Initiate Solana Transfer
POST http://localhost:3001/api/solana/transfer/initiate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "recipientAddress": "11111111111111111111111111111111",
  "amount": 1.5,
  "tokenMint": "EPjFWaLb3ufEKiaBNvv4Ufvj9CxyAz9m4zJWXamBWYh"
}

### Confirm Solana Transfer
POST http://localhost:3001/api/solana/transfer/{{transactionId}}/confirm
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionSignature": "5GQkSN8V5zqxF5E1p7gQQ7Z1vD2vQ3z5x8K2J9L4M6N8P0Q2R4S6T8U0V2W4X6Y8Z"
}

### Get Solana Transaction History
GET http://localhost:3001/api/solana/transactions/history?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Solana Wallets
GET http://localhost:3001/api/user/solana-wallets
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Token Metadata
GET http://localhost:3001/api/solana/token/EPjFWaLb3ufEKiaBNvv4Ufvj9CxyAz9m4zJWXamBWYh/metadata

### Verify Wallet Ownership
POST http://localhost:3001/api/solana/wallet/verify
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "publicKey": "11111111111111111111111111111111",
  "signature": "base64encodedSignature"
}

### Enable 2FA
POST http://localhost:3001/api/user/2fa/enable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Disable 2FA
POST http://localhost:3001/api/user/2fa/disable
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
